Wed Feb 24 12:30:39 1993  greendog  (greendog at amiga)

	* game.c: The 'x' exit hotkey now works while game is in progress.

	* init.c: When minefield starts, "end game" menu item is disabled.

	* init.c: On pubscr, initial window is opened to size specified
	by command line or tooltype.  Previously always opened "small".

Sat Feb 20 21:48:47 1993  greendog  (greendog at amiga)

	* Makefile: When creating the lha archive, the relevant files are
	stored in a "Mine" subdirectory for convenient extraction.

	* game.c: pubscr's game window now has a line separating the time
	and flag counters from the game board.

	* scores.c: pubscr's "score" window and "enter your name" window
	now use Topaz 8.

	* misc.c: pubscr's "game over" window now uses Topaz 8.

	* misc.c: CLI arguments "pubscr" and "noscores" were swapped.
	This is fixed now.

	* misc.c: novice mode defaults to FALSE now. (expert is default)

	* init.c: pubscr window now uses Topaz 8 font instead of system
	default font.

